Hi guys :)

First map :)

I was bored by making all of those advanced de_ and cs_ maps so I just went by and maked a hour project instead :)
it's a big fy_ map  with a lot of spots and camping places.
Hope U enjoi it :D

-------------------------------------------------------------------------


Map includes:

-3D Skybox.
-2D Skybox. (of course.)
-Hint/skip brushes. for NoLagg™ maps :P
-Areaportal brush. for NoLagg™ maps
-Nodraw brush. for NoLagg™ maps
-Buyzones. for more fun :D
-Cubemaps. SO IT LOOKS GOOD!!!

How to install: extract the maps folder to you're programfiles/steam/steamapps/"account-name"/Counter Strike Source/cstrike  <-folder

ty for looking at it :D

NB: Copys of this map will not be tolerated.
